// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3043 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 37f8e84f-f8fc-597e-924e-6dfa35f0730d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
